				<DIV>Instead of looking in a 6-month old (dead) thread, look in the current one that explains what SOE is really doing.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>SOE is not opening the planes to single groups, with a quest or anything else.</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>I refer you to other threads for the details, but it looks like (in summary):</DIV>
<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>
<DIV>You can get gimped into a raid like always. A <EM>few </EM>NO DROP items will drop from the Raid MOB. These items can be used on a quest to get the real flag for the MOB. It does not mean you get all of the flags leading up to it, and you still need to be part of the raid that took it down.</DIV>
				
